summary: not related to the new episode but I need to know, if TJ is the disaster gay and Reed is the Dramatic gay, what kind of gay is...
question: not related to the new episode but I need to know, if TJ is the disaster gay and Reed is the Dramatic gay, what kind of gay is Lester 🤔
answer: Lester would be the casual one.Like, he’s comfortable with his sexuality, but he never really made any big announcement regarding it. Peopleonly know he’s gay when he mentions his boyfriend. He’s not shy about being gay, but he doesn’t think it needs to be made a big deal out of it.He’s very naturally more relaxed then the others, and just let’s things happen. His only not so relaxed moments usually are cause by Reed being an idiot, one he loves, but an idiot nonetheless.
